characterDescription.skinTone: light beige skin with slightly warm undertones, subtle redness around the nose and cheeks
characterDescription.eyeColor: bright cerulean blue with a darker blue limbal ring and subtle gray specks
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, slightly downturned outer corners, medium length dark eyelashes
characterDescription.hairColor: medium brown with ashy undertones, natural lighter brown highlights scattered throughout
characterDescription.hairTexture: wavy to curly, medium thickness strands, prone to frizz
characterDescription.hairStyle: naturally parted slightly to the right, varying lengths and styles. Sometimes worn up in pigtail buns.
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face, developing cheekbones, soft jawline
characterDescription.nose: medium-sized nose with a slightly rounded tip, subtle dorsal hump, and slightly flared nostrils
characterDescription.lips: medium-full lips, slightly more fullness in the bottom lip, natural rose color
characterDescription.smile: wide genuine smile showing top teeth, visible gap between her two front teeth
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium thickness dark brown eyebrows, naturally arched shape, slightly uneven
characterDescription.ears: medium sized ears, visible earlobes, close to head
characterDescription.chin: rounded chin with a small indentation in the center
characterDescription.facialProportions: balanced facial proportions, eyes are approximately one eye-width apart, nose takes up roughly one third of the face length
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: slight gap between two front upper teeth, faint freckles scattered on the bridge of the nose, two small moles on the upper left lip above the lip line
characterDescription.overallImpression: Energetic and expressive appearance, showing a cheerful and playful demeanor.
characterDescription.fullDescription: This child is an 8-9 year old girl with a light beige skin tone and slightly warm undertones. Her eyes are a striking cerulean blue with a darker blue limbal ring. She has medium brown wavy to curly hair with natural lighter highlights and a tendency for frizz. Her face is oval-shaped with developing cheekbones and medium-full lips; a wide smile reveals a distinctive gap between her two front upper teeth. Noteworthy are the faint freckles across the bridge of her nose and the two tiny moles just above her upper left lip.
